# Star Wars API Character Viewer

This project is a simple web application that fetches and displays data from the Star Wars API (SWAPI).

## Features

- Displays data for a Star Wars character including name, height, mass, hair color, skin color, eye color, birth year, and gender.
- Includes a "Next Character" button to fetch and display data for the next character.

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Star Wars API (SWAPI)

## How to Use

1. Clone this repository.
2. Open `index.html` in your web browser.
3. Click the "Next Character" button to display data for the next character.

## Project Structure

- `index.html`: The main HTML file. Includes a section for displaying character data and a "Next Character" button.
- `styles.css`: Contains all the styles for the project.
- `script.js`: Contains the JavaScript code that fetches data from the SWAPI and updates the HTML with the fetched data.

